Hi! Here are these answers: My favorite character in Gauntlet is the warrior. 
My favorite character in Gladiator is the wizard. I named mine  Raistlin 
(after the Dragon lance series). I have only one wizard because he is so 
special. When ever I play Dungeons & Dragons, I always have a character that 
is a mix between a wizard and a warrior.  I want it all. I want to be able to 
carry a sword and do magic. I have never played gauntlet at the arcade. A 
friend just showed it to me after I showed them gladiator. So I have played 
it for a couple of months. I'm glad tht you joined the onelist because your 
fun to talk to! Bye!
